-- Taiwan regulator says to halt review of CTBC's merger plan
-- 
-- Wed Apr 16, 2014 09:08PM EDT
-- None



TAIPEI, April 17 (Reuters) - Taiwan's top financial regulator said on Thursday it will halt the review of CTBC Financial's <2891.TW> merger plan with Taiwan Life Insurance <2833.TW>.

Chairman William Tseng made the comments in a legislative session.